# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:16
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_1bfa8620:

    # "As we work on our assignments in English class, Mrs. McGee comes by my desk and puts her hand on my shoulder."
    "Enquanto trabalhamos nos nossos trabalhos na aula de Inglês, a Sra. McGee aproxima-se da minha secretária e coloca a mão no meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:17
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_e0a44997:

    # et "[pcname], could you stay a bit after class. I need to talk to you about your Canterbury Tales essay."
    et "[pcname], podes ficar um pouco depois da aula? Preciso de falar contigo sobre a tua composição sobre os Contos de Canterbury."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:18
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sim, senhora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:21
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_336feedb:

    # "Through the rest of the class, I worry about what she could want to talk to me about. It has been a week since we finished Canterbury tales, and I thought I did pretty good on that essay."
    "Durante o resto da aula, fico preocupado com o que ela poderá querer falar comigo. Já passou uma semana desde que terminámos os Contos de Canterbury, e achei que me tinha saído bastante bem naquela composição."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:22
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_e846710c:

    # "Finally, class ends and all the other students start out the door, but I stay behind."
    "Finalmente, a aula termina e todos os outros alunos saem pela porta, mas eu fico para trás."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:25
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_91684385:

    # et "Thanks for staying a little late. I just had a couple of questions I wanted to ask you about your essay."
    et "Obrigada por ficares um pouco mais. Só tinha algumas perguntas que queria fazer-te sobre a tua composição."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:26
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:27
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_64a3bccf:

    # et "The assignment was to choose your favorite story from The Canterbury Tales and write a synopsis and an analysis of the story as it relates to modern storytelling."
    et "A tarefa era escolher a tua história favorita de Os Contos de Canterbury e escrever uma sinopse e uma análise da história no que se refere à narrativa moderna."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:28
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_bf5ca486:

    # et "You chose The Miller's Tale. Why is that particular tale your favorite?"
    et "Escolheste O Conto do Moleiro. Por que é que esse conto em particular é o teu favorito?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:33
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_90b318a5:

    # et "Yes, I suppose it is."
    et "Sim, acho que é."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:34
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_5b41f62c:

    # et "It is funny to read about this Miller whose beautiful wife is having sex with men behind his back, and he's completely oblivious."
    et "É engraçado ler sobre este Moleiro cuja bela esposa está a fazer sexo com homens nas suas costas, e ele está completamente alheio a isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:35
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_23f8de94:

    # pc "I was more talking about the fart jokes, but yeah that's pretty funny too."
    pc "Eu estava a referir-me mais às piadas sobre peidos, mas sim, isso também é bastante engraçado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:39
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_589e3574:

    # et "Yes it is."
    et "Sim, é."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:40
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_a1b1b58c:

    # et "I think it's interesting to hear that is the reason why it's your favorite."
    et "Acho interessante saber que essa é a razão pela qual é a tua favorita."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:42
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_225d6c9f:

    # et "I was wondering if it might be your favorite because it's about a man whose beautiful wife is having sex with men behind his back?"
    et "Estava a pensar se seria a tua favorita por ser sobre um homem cuja bela esposa está a fazer sexo com outros homens nas suas costas?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:43
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_5ff3823e:

    # pc "I don't know. Maybe?"
    pc "Não sei. Talvez?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:46
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_47e5b0f5:

    # et "Do you like the idea of having sex with a married woman?"
    et "Gostas da ideia de fazer sexo com uma mulher casada?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:47
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_c4594e48:

    # et "About humiliating her impotent husband? Showing him how a woman should be treated?"
    et "Sobre humilhar o marido impotente dela? Mostrar-lhe como uma mulher deve ser tratada?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:50
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_9a72f950:

    # et "I thought you might."
    et "Achei que sim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:54
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_26f420dd:

    # et "Oh, I'm sorry then. I misread something."
    et "Oh, desculpa então. Interpretei mal alguma coisa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:55
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_bec3fa51:

    # et "The essay is very good. You're doing great in class, [pcname]. I'll stop bothering you about anything… outside of class."
    et "O ensaio está muito bom. Estás a ir muito bem nas aulas, [pcname]. Vou parar de te incomodar com qualquer coisa… fora das aulas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:56
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_d07e9fd4:

    # pc "Okay, Mrs. McGee. I'll talk to you later."
    pc "Está bem, Sra. McGee. Falo contigo mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:57
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_dc1e70f2:

    # et "Bye, [pcname]."
    et "Adeus, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:59
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_491dbae2:

    # "The rest of my classes pass without incident, then it's time to go to work."
    "O resto das minhas aulas decorre sem incidentes, depois é hora de ir trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:63
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_cc5b1913:

    # et "There is a lot of language in the story that is difficult to understand. It's not exactly Old English, it's more like Old English slang."
    et "Há muita linguagem na história que é difícil de compreender. Não é propriamente inglês antigo, é mais como gíria do inglês antigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:64
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_08d83e37:

    # et "Such as the line where Chaucer says that Nicholas grabs Alisoun \"by the queynte.\" Do you understand what that means?"
    et "Como a frase em que Chaucer diz que Nicholas agarra Alisoun «pela queynte». Compreendes o que isso significa?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:69
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_3a9f8ae2:

    # "I lean in and kiss her lips. I half-expect her to pull away from me, but she doesn't. She returns my kiss passionately, her tongue slipping in between my lips."
    "Inclino-me e beijo-lhe os lábios. Quase espero que ela se afaste de mim, mas ela não o faz. Ela retribui o meu beijo apaixonadamente, a sua língua deslizando entre os meus lábios."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:70
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_88e770e5:

    # "She presses herself against me, obviously hungry for more."
    "Ela pressiona-se contra mim, obviamente ansiosa por mais."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:82
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_b851c10c:

    # "I step up to her, reaching down between her legs and grabbing her while pressing my lips against hers."
    "Aproximo-me dela, estendendo a mão entre as suas pernas e agarrando-a enquanto pressiono os meus lábios contra os dela."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:83
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_6836d91b:

    # "I half-expect her to pull away from me, or to yell out, but after the initial surprise of my touch, she starts pressing herself against me, kissing me back with a hunger, grinding her hips against my hand."
    "Quase espero que ela se afaste de mim, ou que grite, mas após a surpresa inicial do meu toque, ela começa a pressionar-se contra mim, retribuindo o beijo com fome, esfregando as ancas contra a minha mão."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:84
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_a8ed1eb1:

    # "I could feel how warm and wet she was even through her dress."
    "Conseguia sentir o quão quente e molhada ela estava, mesmo através do vestido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:86
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_75e7549b:

    # et "That's too bad."
    et "É uma pena."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:89
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_ebc0b6c6:

    # et "Okay, [pcname], that's all I wanted to ask you. Your essay is very good and you're doing great in class."
    et "Muito bem, [pcname], era só isto que te queria perguntar. A tua redação está muito boa e estás a ir muito bem nas aulas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:90
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_367c3a3f:

    # et "You better get to your next class now."
    et "É melhor ires para a tua próxima aula agora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:91
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_1ca80c77_1:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sim, senhora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:92
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_56ef2b64:

    # "I leave her class and walk to the next, not exactly sure what all of that was about."
    "Saio da aula dela e caminho para a próxima, sem saber bem o que foi tudo aquilo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:93
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_f32bd31b:

    # "The rest of my classes pass without incident, then it is time to go to work."
    "O resto das minhas aulas passa sem incidentes, depois é hora de ir para o trabalho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:99
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_eb447035:

    # "Then, just as quickly and passionately as her kiss started, it ends when she forcefully pushes me away."
    "Então, tão rápida e apaixonadamente como o beijo dela começou, ele termina quando ela me empurra com força."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:100
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_815cee6e:

    # et "No, [pcname]. We can't do this. I'm married and I love my husband."
    et "Não, [pcname]. Não podemos fazer isto. Sou casada e amo o meu marido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:101
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_bbb49d81:

    # pc "But…"
    pc "Mas…"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:102
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_baa067de:

    # et "No buts. You should go."
    et "Sem mas. Deves ir."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:103
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_6d9994c4:

    # pc "I don't understand."
    pc "Não compreendo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:104
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_4f85d033:

    # et "This is not the time or place for this sort of outburst. We won't be discussing this anymore right now."
    et "Este não é o momento nem o local para este tipo de explosão. Não vamos discutir mais isto agora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:105
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_1f1c51ca:

    # et "Your essay is very good and you're doing great in class. Now get to your next class, we're done here."
    et "A tua redação está muito boa e estás a ir muito bem nas aulas. Agora vai para a tua próxima aula, terminámos por aqui."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:106
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_f72d2804:

    # pc "Uh… okay. Bye, Mrs. McGee."
    pc "Uh… está bem. Adeus, Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:109
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_0ccd1147:

    # "I leave her classroom, not exactly sure what had just happened."
    "Saio da sala de aula dela, sem saber bem o que acabou de acontecer."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:110
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_213f5c51:

    # "She's playing some sort of game and it feels like I'm just along for the ride."
    "Ela está a jogar algum tipo de jogo e parece que eu estou apenas a acompanhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:111
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_78fe728d:

    # "I guess I'll have to wait and see what happens next."
    "Acho que vou ter de esperar para ver o que acontece a seguir."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee7.rpy:114
translate portuguese mrsmcgee7_0d69ab43:

    # "I go to my next class and the rest of the day passes without incident, then it's time to go to work."
    "Vou para a minha próxima aula e o resto do dia passa sem incidentes, depois é hora de ir trabalhar."

